The paper deals with machine learning and optimization techniques for computing low dimensional representations that are robust to adversarial perturbations. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and statistics (cs.ST).
